  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "We have bucket defined in lodestar-db so all project using lodestar-db shares bucket space and has to edit lodestar-db files.\r\n\r\nWe could have 1byte app prefix like:\r\n```\r\nenum AppBucket {\r\n   bn = 1;\r\n   validator = 3;\r\n   lightclient = 2;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nSo db key would be: `app (1 byte) + repository (4 byte) + id (x bytes)`\r\n\r\nThat way, each app could share same db and maintain it's own repository buckets without interference.",
